      An Open Label, Safety Study to Assess the Potential for Adrenal Suppression Following
      Treatment with DSXS in Patients with Atopic Dermatitis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the potential of DSXS topical product to suppress HPA axis function in patients
      with moderate to severe atopic dermatitis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
